title: 652. Breaking Down the Rumored Rift Between Seahawks & Russell Wilson + David Cutcliffe Joins
itunes:title: 652. Breaking Down the Rumored Rift Between Seahawks & Russell Wilson + David Cutcliffe Joins
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys break down a report by The Athletic saying there's a rift between the Seattle Seahawks and quarterback Russell Wilson (:28). Then, Duke head coach David Cutcliffe joins, as he discusses the challenges due to the pandemic, the importance of athleticism in a quarterback, touches on Duke prospects and gives his take on Clemson quarterback Trevor Lawrence (12:59). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
